WF-002 | Open Edit Activity Settings from column menu | actor: Teacher | branch: none | terminal: Edit Activity Settings | on_success: open activity grade settings
WF-003 | Save inline edits while Edit mode is enabled | actor: Teacher | branch: Edit_Mode_Control == true | terminal: Save changes | on_success: persist inline grade edits
</workflows>

